\v 38 Kwasekubethelwa abaphangi ababili\x + 27.44. 26.55.\x* kanye laye, omunye ngakwesokunene lomunye ngakwesokhohlo\x + Luka 23.32,33. Joha. 19.18.\x*.
\v 39 Labadlulayo\x + Hlab. 22.7; 109.25. Luka 23.35. Jobe 16.4.\x* bamhlambaza\x + Luka 22.65.\x*, benikina amakhanda abo\x + Jer. 18.16. Lilo 2.15. Zef. 2.15. Mark. 15.29. Hlab. 22.7; 109.25. Luka 23.35. Jobe 16.4.\x*,
\v 40 besithi: Wena odiliza ithempeli ulakhe ngensuku ezintathu, zisindise\x + 26.61. Mark. 14.58. Joha. 2.19.\x*; uba uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu, yehla esiphambanweni\x + 27.43. 26.63. Luka 4.23.\x*.
