\v 42 Wasindisa abanye, yena angezisindise. Uba eyiNkosi yakoIsrayeli, kehle khathesi esiphambanweni, futhi sizamkholwa\x + Joha. 1.49. Luka 23.37.\x*.
\v 43 Wathemba kuNkulunkulu; kamkhulule khathesi, uba emthanda\x + Hlab. 22.8.\x*. Ngoba wathi: NgiyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + 27.43. 26.63. Luka 4.23.\x*.
