\v 47 Njalo abanye kwababemi khona besizwa bathi: Lo ubiza uElija.
\v 48 Njalo omunye wabo wahle wagijima, wathatha uzipho, wa\add lu\add*gcwalisa ngeviniga\x + 27.34. Hlab. 69.21. Luka 23.36. Joha. 19.29.\x*, wa\add lu\add*hloma emhlangeni, wamnika ukuthi anathe\x + Joha. 19.29.\x*.
\v 49 Kodwa abanye bathi: Yekelani sibone ukuthi uElija uzakuza amsindise\x + Mark. 15.36.\x*.
