\v 54 Kwathi induna yekhulu lalabo ababelayo belinde uJesu\x + 27.36.\x*, sebebonile ukuzamazama komhlaba\x + 27.54. 28.2.\x* lezinto ezenzekileyo, besaba kakhulu\x + Mark. 15.39.\x*, bathi: Ngeqiniso lo ubeyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + Luka 23.47.\x*.
