\v 55 Kwakukhona lapho abesifazana abanengi bebukele\x + Luka 23.49. Joha. 19.25.\x* bekhatshana\x + Hlab. 38.11.\x*, ababemlandele uJesu bevela eGalili\x + Luka 8.2,3.\x*, bemncedisa\x + 25.44.\x*;
